Source URL:
- https://docs.mistral.ai/api/endpoint/ocr
Fetched: 2026-02-27

OCR API facts:
- OCR endpoint: POST /v1/ocr
- Full URL: https://api.mistral.ai/v1/ocr
- Auth header: Authorization: Bearer <MISTRAL_API_KEY>
- Content-Type: application/json
- Document supports document_url, image_url, file_id flows.
- Response includes model, pages[], usage_info, document_annotation.

Implementation implications:
- Keep /v1/ocr explicit in OCR provider calls.
- Keep retry logic on 408/425/429/5xx.
- Parse pages[].markdown defensively and reject empty OCR output.
